Package com.landawn.abacus.util

Class DateUtil.DTF

java.lang.Object
com.landawn.abacus.util.DateUtil.DTF
Enclosing class:
DateUtil
public static final class DateUtil.DTF extends Object
The major purpose of this class is to get rid of the milliseconds part: .SSS or nanoseconds part: .SSSSSS
